  "texts": [
    "Carvalho et al. (2020) present a CV work-flow using Semantic Segmentation (SS) neural networks.",
    "The workflow uses MicroCT to scan samples and a fully automated identification followed by a deep SS-CNN to segment the fossils.",
    "This proposed pipeline has noteworthy results, although is specific to certain resources (e.g., MicroCT datasets).",
    "Yu et al. (2022) introduce a DL approach for segmenting CT scans of protoceratopsian dinosaur fossils, utilizing a modified DeepLab v3+ network with MobileNet v1 as the feature extractor.",
    "The application of atrous spatial pyramid pooling (ASPP) and multi-scale feature recognition allowed the model to achieve high segmentation accuracy, significantly reducing the time needed for manual annotation."
  ],
